* CNX tags + active tag movement
COLOR DEFAULT
USE students noindex
SETCNX students.cnx
STATUS
* pick LNAME asc
SETORDER students.cnx TAG LNAME --asc
STATUS
STRUCT INDEX
LIST
* flip to GPA desc
SETORDER students.cnx TAG GPA --desc
STATUS
STRUCT INDEX
LIST
* go back to LNAME asc (ASCEND only flips direction, not tag)
SETORDER students.cnx TAG LNAME --asc
STATUS
LIST
* end
